OL,3,CNHS health leaders planning staff cuts
OL,4,Cto balance the books
OL,6,FThe majority of health leaders are
OL,7,Fconsidering cutting clinical and non-
OL,8,Fclinical staff to balance their books,
OL,9,Fa new survey has found ` with warnings
OL,10,Fthis could hinder efforts to tackle
OL,11,Fwaiting lists.
OL,13,FExperts said strict targets are
OL,14,Fforcing services to take "drastic
OL,15,Fmeasures" and focus on short-term
OL,16,Fsolutions rather than a long-term plan
OL,17,Fto bolster services.
