OL,3,CNHS health leaders planning staff cuts
OL,4,Cto balance the books
OL,6,FOne NHS boss also described their
OL,7,Ffinancial position as "very difficult"
OL,8,Fin the face of "extraordinary levels
OL,9,Fof demand".
OL,11,FThe survey of 110 health leaders by
OL,12,FNHS Confederation included responses
OL,13,Ffrom bosses of NHS trusts, integrated
OL,14,Fcare boards (ICBs), primary care
OL,15,Fservices and voluntary organisations
OL,16,Fproviding NHS services.
