OL,3,CNHS health leaders planning staff cuts
OL,4,Cto balance the books
OL,6,FSome 67% of leaders from NHS trusts
OL,7,Fand ICBs said they are planning to let
OL,8,Fsome clinical staff go to meet saving
OL,9,Ftargets, with 90% saying they will
OL,10,Freduce their non-clinical headcount.
OL,12,FIn primary care, some 74% of leaders
OL,13,Falso said they will have to cut
OL,14,Fclinical staff, with 79% planning to
OL,15,Flet non-clinical staff go.It comes
OL,16,Fafter the Government announced an
OL,17,Fadditional #2.5 billion for the NHS in
OL,18,F2024/25 as part of the spring budget
OL,19,Fin March.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/15
