OL,3,CNHS health leaders planning staff cuts
OL,4,Cto balance the books
OL,6,FAt the time, NHS Confederation chief
OL,7,Fexecutive Matthew Taylor described the
OL,8,Fsum as "at best flat in real terms
OL,9,Fagainst a backdrop of significant
OL,10,Fdeficits and universal pressures".The
OL,11,Fhealth service also has an annual
OL,12,Fefficiency ` or cost savings ` target
OL,13,Fof 2.2% for the period.
OL,15,FHowever, leaders told NHS
OL,16,FConfederation that they would need to
OL,17,Fmake savings of 6% for the year, with
OL,18,Ftargets for local services ranging
OL,19,Ffrom 1.6% to 11%.
