OL,3,CNHS health leaders planning staff cuts
OL,4,Cto balance the books
OL,6,FMr Taylor said: "The NHS is operating
OL,7,Funder immense financial strain, with
OL,8,Flocal services having to consider some
OL,9,Fdrastic measures to balance their
OL,10,Fbooks this year. This will disrupt
OL,11,Fplans to improve patient care and
OL,12,Freduce waiting lists.
OL,26,@nD@QOU
