OL,3,CNHS health leaders planning staff cuts
OL,4,Cto balance the books
OL,6,F"But it is also forcing NHS leaders to
OL,7,Ffocus on delivering immediate cuts to
OL,8,Fachieve stringent efficiency targets
OL,9,Fover the long-term transformation of
OL,10,Fservices that they want to be focusing
OL,11,Fon, we in fact, know this has already
OL,12,Fbeen happening in some trusts. Put
OL,13,Fsimply, this is not an effective way
OL,14,Fto run local services."
OL,16,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak pledged to
OL,17,Fcut waiting lists in January 2023,
OL,18,Falthough the figure continued to rise
OL,19,Fin the months that followed, reaching
OL,20,Fa record high in September before
OL,21,Ffalling slightly.
