OL,3,CNHS health leaders planning staff cuts
OL,4,Cto balance the books
OL,6,FThe latest data from NHS England shows
OL,7,Fan estimated 7.54 million treatments
OL,8,Fwere waiting to be carried out at the
OL,9,Fend of March 2024, relating to 6.29
OL,10,Fmillion patients.
OL,12,FHealth minister Andrew Stephenson
OL,13,Fsaid: "The Conservatives have taken
OL,14,Fbold action to cut waiting lists and
OL,15,Fsecure the future of the NHS, with the
OL,16,Ftotal budget increasing by over a
OL,17,Fthird in real terms since 2010 and our
OL,18,F#2.4 billion long-term workforce plan
OL,19,F` the first of its kind ` delivering
OL,20,Frecord numbers of doctors and nurses.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
