OL,3,CNHS health leaders planning staff cuts
OL,4,Cto balance the books
OL,6,F"Meanwhile Labour's NHS spending
OL,7,Fcommitments are completely unfunded,
OL,8,Fwhich would push up taxes on hard-
OL,9,Fworking people and delay patients
OL,10,Fgetting the care they need.
OL,12,F"Only Rishi Sunak and the
OL,13,FConservatives have a clear plan and
OL,14,Fwill take the bold action necessary to
OL,15,Fcut waiting lists and deliver for
OL,16,Fpatients. Sir Keir Starmer would put
OL,17,Four progress at risk and take the
OL,18,Fcountry back to square one."
