OL,6,FEarlier this week, Sir Keir Starmer
OL,7,Fvowed that reducing the list would be
OL,8,Fthe "first step" of a Labour
OL,9,Fgovernment's plans to get the NHS
OL,10,F"back on its feet".
OL,12,FElsewhere, two thirds of trust and ICB
OL,13,Fleaders who responded to the survey
OL,14,Fsaid further strikes would also add to
OL,15,Fthe pressure of meeting targets.
