OL,6,FIt comes after the British Medical
OL,7,FAssociation (BMA) announced on
OL,8,FWednesday that junior doctors will
OL,9,Fwalk out from 7am on June 27 until 7am
OL,10,Fon July 2, days before the General
OL,11,FElection.
OL,13,FOverall, NHS strikes are estimated to
OL,14,Fhave led to the cancellation of 1.4
OL,15,Fmillion appointments and procedures,
OL,16,Fand have cost the health service about
OL,17,F#3 billion.
