OL,6,FThe poll also revealed most leaders
OL,7,Fwill deliver their budgets by freezing
OL,8,Fvacancies or slashing spending on
OL,9,Fagency locums or bank staff.
OL,11,FFigures from NHS Digital show there
OL,12,Fwere 100,658 vacancies in England in
OL,13,Fthe three months to March 2024.
OL,15,FSix in 10 NHS leaders also said they
OL,16,Fwill need top-up funding from the
OL,17,FGovernment within a year to hit
OL,18,Ftargets, while six in 10 trust and ICB
OL,19,Fleaders said they could not meet their
OL,20,Ftargets without more investment.
