OL,6,FOne NHS trust chair described its
OL,7,F"financial position is really
OL,8,Fdifficult" with the expectation of
OL,9,Fmaking "very substantial efficiency
OL,10,Fsavings, larger than the NHS has ever
OL,11,Fachieved, at the same time as facing
OL,12,Fextraordinary levels of demand".
OL,14,FAn NHS chief executive also said they
OL,15,Fdid not believe it was possible to
OL,16,Fdeliver every financial, performance,
OL,17,Fworkforce, quality and safety targets,
OL,18,Fadding "something has to give".
