OL,6,FMr Taylor added: "While NHS leaders
OL,7,Fknow they must continue to run their
OL,8,Fservices as efficiently as possible,
OL,9,Fthis is the tightest financial
OL,10,Fposition the NHS has faced in years.
OL,12,F"This type of short-term planning
OL,13,Fhinders the NHS's ability to plan
OL,14,Fservices and it represents poor value
OL,15,Ffor money for taxpayers."
OL,17,FIn February, NHS Confederation
OL,18,Fpublished a manifesto highlighting
OL,19,Ffive key areas for the next government
OL,20,Fto prioritise.
