OL,6,FThese included a hike in NHS capital
OL,7,Fspending across the UK ` with an
OL,8,Fincrease of #6.4 billion for England
OL,9,Falone ` as well as a commitment to
OL,10,Ffunding the NHS Long Term Workforce
OL,11,FPlan and an equivalent blueprint for
OL,12,Fsocial care.
OL,14,FMr Taylor said: "NHS productivity is
OL,15,Fbeing held back by reasons beyond the
OL,16,Fimmediate gift of the NHS to control,
OL,17,Fsuch as insufficient capacity in
OL,18,Fsocial care and low levels capital
OL,19,Finvestment.
